Package: RDCF
Title: Comparable Company Analysis (Comps) Valuation in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeb", "Dee", , "jeb.dee@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Performs a complete Comparable Company Analysis (Comps) valuation
    on any publicly traded company using real financial data pulled from Yahoo
    Finance. Given a stock ticker, the package automatically identifies peer
    companies in the same industry, retrieves key valuation multiples
    (P/E, EV/EBITDA, P/S, P/B), and produces an implied valuation range for
    the target company based on where its peers trade.
